Text: Cohen & Steers Select Pref & Inc Fd, Inc (NYSE:PSF) to Issue $0.17 Dividend Cohen & Steers Select Pref & Inc Fd, Inc (NYSE:PSF) announced a dividend on Tuesday, June 11th, NASDAQ reports.
